      {
        "key": "蹦蹦炸彈",
        "title": "蹦蹦炸彈",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/ce0014e0d25cd397fef22aafb4b411c0_7758685458279206659.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n造成3點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> ，本角色附屬 <color=#ffffff>爆裂火花</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>爆裂火花</color>\n<color=#ffd780>狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>所附屬角色進行重擊時：</color> 少花費1個 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，并且傷害+1。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：1</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "轟轟火花",
        "title": "轟轟火花",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/3f2b5db15d922d53d7d4db8261138f17_5652517973764318266.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成3點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> ，在對方場上生成 <color=#ffffff>轟轟火花</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>轟轟火花</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>我方角色使用技能後：</color> 對我方出戰角色造成2點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害·其一",
        "title": "火元素傷害·其一",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/13/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4207913581323829846.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素+</color> <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>蒸發</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超載</color> ：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害·其二",
        "title": "火元素傷害·其二",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/13/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3049434426791303412.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>燃燒</color> ：本傷害+1，召喚 <color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffd780>召喚物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>結束階段：</color> 造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</color>"
          }
        ],
